Go get it!

552
00:52:22,805 --> 00:52:24,045
Pedal to the metal!

553
00:52:39,085 --> 00:52:40,205
Hello?

554
00:52:42,605 --> 00:52:43,605
What did you say?

555
00:52:51,805 --> 00:52:52,925
Weiling, it's gonna be okay.

556
00:52:53,805 --> 00:52:55,125
The doctor will be with you soon.

557
00:53:15,885 --> 00:53:16,885
Dear.

558
00:53:21,445 --> 00:53:22,445
Dear!

559
00:53:25,045 --> 00:53:26,045
Dear.

560
00:53:26,925 --> 00:53:27,925
Lalin?

561
00:53:52,405 --> 00:53:53,405
Lalin!

562
00:53:54,045 --> 00:53:55,605
Where are you? Who did this to you?!

563
00:53:55,645 --> 00:53:58,005
If you don't bring Pin to me by tonight,

564
00:54:00,325 --> 00:54:01,525
there's no reason

565
00:54:01,725 --> 00:54:03,045
for me to let Ms. Lalin live.

566
00:54:04,805 --> 00:54:06,485
It all started with me,

567
00:54:06,725 --> 00:54:08,245
so it has to end with me.

568
00:54:18,125 --> 00:54:19,125
Arisa!

569
00:54:19,325 --> 00:54:20,325
Ow!

570
00:54:21,885 --> 00:54:23,245
How could you do this to Lalin?

571
00:54:23,485 --> 00:54:24,725
How could you?!

572
00:54:26,805 --> 00:54:27,805
Arisa!

573
00:54:27,845 --> 00:54:29,085
Help!

574
00:54:35,685 --> 00:54:36,805
You tricked me!

575
00:54:42,245 --> 00:54:44,165
It's all over now, sweetheart.

576
00:54:47,845 --> 00:54:51,941
♫ Never a second could I forget you ♫

577
00:54:51,965 --> 00:54:55,541
♫ You're still here when
night comes through ♫

578
00:54:55,565 --> 00:54:59,885
♫ I don't wish to wake up sometimes, ♫

579
00:54:59,925 --> 00:55:03,421
♫ Afraid that you'd say goodbye ♫

580
00:55:03,445 --> 00:55:07,221
♫ I dream of another rendezvous ♫

581
00:55:07,245 --> 00:55:15,245
♫ To say that I'll never stop missing you ♫

582
00:55:15,725 --> 00:55:21,285
♫ Since you're my whole heart ♫

583
00:55:44,565 --> 00:55:50,005
♫ Do you know I miss you? ♫
